graph TB
    style LLM fill:#45B7D1,color:#000
    style GW fill:#6C5CE7,color:#fff
    style REG fill:#4ECDC4,color:#000
    style C fill:#96CEB4,color:#000
    style S fill:#FFEAA7,color:#000
    style W fill:#FF8C42,color:#000

    LLM[LLM Client\nJSON-RPC 2.0\ntools/list or tools/call] --> GW[MCPGatewayWorkflow\nTenant validation\nDurable session]
    GW --> REG[ToolRegistryActor\nSchema validation\nUsage tracking]
    REG --> C[CalculatorToolActor\nArithmetic]
    REG --> S[SearchToolActor\nKV-backed document search]
    REG --> W[WeatherToolActor\nSimulated weather data]
